1. *Pričaš* li o njoj? (Are you talking about her?) 
2. On ne *pričaš* ništa. (He is not saying anything.)
3. Oni su dugo *pričaš*li. (They talked for a long time.) 
4. Ona je sve *pričaš*la. (She was talking about everything.) 
5. Oni su svi *pričaš*li. (They were all talking.) 
6. Ja sam *pričaš*o o njoj. (I was talking about her.) 
7. Oni su *pričaš*ali o njoj. (They were talking about her.) 
8. Ona je *pričaš*la sa njim. (She was talking to him.)